---
// src/pages/privacy.astro — Privacy Policy
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "@/components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "@/components/Footer.astro";
import LeftSidebar from "@/components/LeftSidebar.astro";
import { SITE } from "@/config";
import { getLang, useTranslations, LANG_TO_PATH } from "@/i18n/ui";

const lang = getLang(Astro.url);
const t = useTranslations(lang);
const isZh = lang === "zh-CN" || lang === "zh-TW";
---

<Layout title={`${isZh ? "隐私政策" : "Privacy Policy"} | ${SITE.title}`} description={isZh ? "Bitaigen 隐私政策" : "Bitaigen Privacy Policy"}>
  <Header />
  <div class="site-outer">
    <LeftSidebar />
    <main class="main-col" style="padding:20px 20px 60px;" id="main-content">
      <article class="app-prose" style="max-width:720px;">
        {isZh ? (
          <Fragment>
            <h1>隐私政策</h1>
            <p><strong>最后更新：2026 年 3 月</strong></p>

            <p>Bitaigen（以下简称"本站"）非常重视您的隐私。本隐私政策说明了当您访问 <a href={SITE.website}>{SITE.website}</a> 时，我们如何收集、使用和保护您的信息。</p>

            <h2>1. 信息收集</h2>
            <p>本站可能收集以下类型的信息：</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>自动收集的信息</strong>：浏览器类型、访问时间、页面浏览量、引荐来源等匿名分析数据。</li>
              <li><strong>Cookies</strong>：用于记住您的语言偏好和主题设置。</li>
              <li><strong>您主动提供的信息</strong>：如通过联系表单或电子邮件提供的姓名和电子邮件地址。</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>2. 信息使用</h2>
            <p>我们收集的信息仅用于：</p>
            <ul>
              <li>改善网站内容和用户体验</li>
              <li>分析网站流量和使用趋势</li>
              <li>回复您的咨询和反馈</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>3. 第三方服务</h2>
            <p>本站使用以下第三方服务，它们可能收集相关数据：</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>网站分析</strong>：用于了解网站访问情况（匿名数据）。</li>
              <li><strong>CoinGecko / Binance API</strong>：用于获取实时加密货币价格，不涉及用户个人数据。</li>
              <li><strong>Ghost CMS</strong>：用于内容管理和文章发布。</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>4. 联盟营销披露</h2>
            <p>本站与币安（Binance）存在联盟合作关系。当您通过本站的推荐链接注册币安账户时，本站可能获得佣金。这不会影响您的注册费用或交易成本。</p>

            <h2>5. 数据安全</h2>
            <p>我们采取合理的技术和组织措施来保护您的信息安全，但请注意，互联网传输无法保证 100% 安全。</p>

            <h2>6. 儿童隐私</h2>
            <p>本站不面向 18 岁以下的未成年人。我们不会故意收集未成年人的个人信息。</p>

            <h2>7. 政策变更</h2>
            <p>本隐私政策可能不时更新。更新后的政策将在本页面发布，并更新"最后更新"日期。</p>

            <h2>8. 联系我们</h2>
            <p>如有任何隐私相关问题，请联系：</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Email: <a href="mailto:contact@bitaigen.com">contact@bitaigen.com</a></li>
              <li>Telegram: <a href={SITE.telegram} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@AllenAmbrose</a></li>
            </ul>
          </Fragment>
        ) : (
          <Fragment>
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p><strong>Last updated: March 2026</strong></p>

            <p>Bitaigen ("we", "us", "our") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit <a href={SITE.website}>{SITE.website}</a>.</p>

            <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Automatically collected data</strong>: Browser type, visit time, page views, referral sources, and other anonymous analytics data.</li>
              <li><strong>Cookies</strong>: Used to remember your language preference and theme setting.</li>
              <li><strong>Information you provide</strong>: Name and email address if you contact us directly.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>
            <ul>
              <li>To improve website content and user experience</li>
              <li>To analyze traffic and usage trends</li>
              <li>To respond to your inquiries</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>3. Third-Party Services</h2>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Analytics</strong>: Anonymous website traffic analysis.</li>
              <li><strong>CoinGecko / Binance API</strong>: For real-time cryptocurrency prices — no personal data involved.</li>
              <li><strong>Ghost CMS</strong>: Content management and publishing.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>4. Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
            <p>We participate in the Binance affiliate program. When you sign up for Binance through our referral links, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you.</p>

            <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
            <p>We implement reasonable measures to protect your information. However, no internet transmission is 100% secure.</p>

            <h2>6. Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p>This website is not intended for persons under 18. We do not knowingly collect information from minors.</p>

            <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Updates will be posted on this page with a revised "Last updated" date.</p>

            <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
            <ul>
              <li>Email: <a href="mailto:contact@bitaigen.com">contact@bitaigen.com</a></li>
              <li>Telegram: <a href={SITE.telegram} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@AllenAmbrose</a></li>
            </ul>
          </Fragment>
        )}
      </article>
    </main>
  </div>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
